{
  "stem": "21139.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we-- after a couple days, we landed in Gurs camp, the Gurs in France.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They took us off a train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took us then by truck to that-- to the camps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all we saw was barracks, I don't know how many.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They separated men and women.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I stayed with my mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My father was in a different area.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the mud was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had one pair of shoes on, which stuck in the mud.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And after that, I wore what-- whoever gave me something, whatever I could.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I don't know what it is, but sometimes the little miracles do happen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we-- they took us in a-- in a barrack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there were some Gypsies.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I guess some of them were very handy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They had some woods and thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there was only the cement floor, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There were no beds or anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was a little bit of straw here and there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But one man came in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My mother and I, we were standing inside that door.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And that-- one of the Gypsies, the men, gave my mother one-- a a bed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was not a bed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was just something off the floor, with some-- some wood nailed together.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "At least she didn't have to lay on the cement floor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And so how this just happened and how-- no one knows or can explain.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were in that camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at night, we were so hungry we couldn't sleep.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were watching the mice and the rats going up and down the poles.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we used to get one loaf of bread for I don't remember how many people were in that one barrack.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
